item.title: Food Trucks in the Research Park
item.description:
It's summer time and that means food trucks are making their way to the Research Park!

The schedule, times and locations for the trucks change so please check out our Food Truck webpage for the most up to date information http://researchpark.illinois.edu/FoodTrucks

item.title: CU Bike to Work Day
item.description:
Help make the Research Park the greenest place in CU! T-shirts, beverages and breakfast food will be available on a first come, first served basis.

Register TODAY! https://secure.lglforms.com/form_engine/s/0Lxq54h1rZUO8siiwX90FA
